            </a>

          </li>


        </ul>



      </div>

      <div class="d-flex flex-column  align-items-left align-items-sm-start side-menu-list">

        <ul class="nav nav-pills flex-column align-items-sm-left px-3 side-menu-list1" id="menu">
          <li>
            <a href="#" class="nav-link align-start px-0" style="padding-top:40px">
              <span class="ms-1 sidemenu-buttons side-menu"><i class="bi bi-egg-fill"></i> Food
              </span>
            </a>
          </li>

          <li>
            <a href="#submenu5" data-bs-toggle="collapse" class="nav-link px-0 align-left ">
              <span class="ms-1 sidemenu-buttons side-menu "><i class="bi bi-bell-fill"></i> Quiz</span></i></a>

          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="#submenu6" data-bs-toggle="collapse" class="nav-link px-0 align-left">
              <span class="ms-1 sidemenu-buttons side-menu"><i class="bi bi-pin-map-fill"></i> Cuisine</span>
            </a>

          </li>



        </ul>



      </div>


    </div>



    <!-- Page Content -->
    <div id="content">
      <!-- We'll fill this with dummy content -->

      <div class="menu py-5 bg-light p-5">
        <h4 class="text-center">Hello <%= user.firstname %> , Pave your way into our Culinary world!!</h4>
        <h2>Dashboard</h2><br>
        <div class="container-fluid">
          <div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-md-3 g-5 justify-content-center">
            <div class="col">
              <div class="card shadow-sm text-center h-100">
                <img src="images/food.png" class="card-img-top" alt="Food">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <h5 class="card-title">Food</h5>
                  <p class="card-text">Look up about different ingredients, its nutritional value and possible
                    recipes with it.</p>
                  <a href="#" class="btn btn-success">GO!</a>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col">
              <div class="card shadow-sm text-center h-100">
                <img src="images/quiz.png" class="card-img-top" alt="Quiz">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <h5 class="card-title">Quiz</h5>
                  <p class="card-text">Take a quiz to know your current preferred food ingredients without
                    thinking much about it!</p>
                  <a href="/activities" class="btn btn-success">GO!</a>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col">
              <div class="card shadow-sm text-center h-100">
                <img src="images/search_recipe.png" class="card-img-top" alt="Search Recipe">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <h5 class="card-title">Search Recipes</h5>
                  <p class="card-text">Get to know different recipes using specific ingredients.</p>
                  <a href="/search" class="btn btn-success">GO!</a>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col">
              <div class="card shadow-sm text-center h-100">
                <img src="images/cuisine.png" class="card-img-top" alt="Cuisine">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <h5 class="card-title">Cuisine</h5>
                  <p class="card-text">Get to know about different recipes from unique cuisines.</p>
                  <a href="#" class="btn btn-success">GO!</a>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col">
              <div class="card shadow-sm text-center h-100">
                <img src="images/meal.png" class="card-img-top" alt="Meal">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <h5 class="card-title">Meal</h5>
                  <p class="card-text">Finding it hard to decide what to have for Breakfast, Lunch or Dinner?
                    Know what recipes are healthy and mostly eaten at different food time zones.</p>
                  <a href="#" class="btn btn-success">GO!</a>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
